Question
========
Ilayda wants to know if weakly gifted students who receive extra support within regular education have different cognitive development than weakly gifted students who do not receive extra support. She conducts a repeated measures ANOVA. What effect in the SPSS output should she look at to answer her question?

Answerlist
----------
* *Within-Subject* effect of "Time."
* *Within-Subject* effect of "Time*Support."
* *Within-Subject* effect of "Support".
* *Between-Subject* effect of "Support".
